questions.quote: Sweetie, you know I have no sense of humor when it comes to the wedding.
Oh, y'know what? Maybe uh, you...you should come to me. I'm a not, I'm not wearing any bottoms.
...you were 50 minutes late to the class, what did you crawl there?!
Are you angry at me because I said your handwriting is childlike?
Ok well, before you do, I know we weren't supposed to get you going away presents, but I do have something for you.
Why would you start again after chewing all that quitting gum?
I know, but, I made a huge mistake. I never should have broken up with her. Will you help me? Please?
